We need dry or sukya bhajya for lunch box. There is no masala or vatan for such sabzis. For the sabzi to be tasty we need some masala for such sabzis. Here is recipe for sukya or dry sabzi masala. You can store it for about a month. You can use this masala for any dry sabzi. It tastes nice. You can try this recipe at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
‚Ä¢ 1/4 cup Besan
‚Ä¢ 1/2 cup Peanuts
‚Ä¢ Few Curry leaves
‚Ä¢ 10~12 Garlic cloves
‚Ä¢ 1/4 cup shredded dry Coconut
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp Cumin seeds
‚Ä¢ 1/4 tsp Fenugreek seeds
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp Kala masala
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp Red chili powder
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ 1/2 tsp Sugar
‚Ä¢ 2 tsp Oil
‚Ä¢ Finely chopped Onion
‚Ä¢ 4 medium size chopped Capsicum
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ Finely chopped Coriander leaves

Method:
‚Ä¢ Heat up a pan on medium heat and add besan. 
‚Ä¢ Dry roast besan a little until it begins to get light golden color. 
‚Ä¢ You can add oil if you want. 
‚Ä¢ Transfer the besan into a dish. 
‚Ä¢ In the same pan add peanuts, curry leaves, garlic and roast everything well together. 
‚Ä¢ You can skip curry leaves if you don‚Äôt like. 
‚Ä¢ When peanuts are roasted well add dry coconut, cumin seeds and roast well until coconut 
  changes the color a little. 
‚Ä¢ When coconut turns light golden, turn off the gas and add fenugreek seeds. 
‚Ä¢ Transfer all the roasted ingredients into a blender jar and add kala masala, red chili powder, 
  salt, sugar and blend into a little coarse powder. 
‚Ä¢ You can use garam masala, goda masala or any other masala that you use regularly in place 
  of kala masala. 
‚Ä¢ You can use gudh in place of sugar or completely skip sugar too. 
‚Ä¢ Masala is ready. 
‚Ä¢ Heat up oil in a pan. 
‚Ä¢ Add onion and fry until it turns light golden. 
‚Ä¢ You can skip onion if you don‚Äôt like. 
‚Ä¢ When onion begins to turn light golden add capsicum and mix well. 
‚Ä¢ Cover and steam for about 6-7 minutes. 
‚Ä¢ Mix well at the regular intervals of 2-3 minutes. 
‚Ä¢ After about 6-7 minutes when capsicum is almost cooked add salt and mix well. 
‚Ä¢ Add 2-3 tsp masala that we blended and mix well. 
‚Ä¢ Cover and steam the sabzi on low heat for about 3-4 minutes.  
‚Ä¢ Add coriander leaves and mix well. 
‚Ä¢ Dhobli mirachi sabzi is all ready.

‚Ä¢ 1/2 tsp Sugar
‚Ä¢ 2 tsp Oil
‚Ä¢ Finely chopped Onion
‚Ä¢ 4 medium size chopped Capsicum
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ Finely chopped Coriander leaves

Method:
‚Ä¢ Heat up a pan on medium heat and add besan. 
‚Ä¢ Dry roast besan a little until it begins to get light golden color. 
‚Ä¢ You can add oil if you want. 
‚Ä¢ Transfer the besan into a dish. 
‚Ä¢ In the same pan add peanuts, curry leaves, garlic and roast everything well together. 
‚Ä¢ You can skip curry leaves if you don‚Äôt like. 
‚Ä¢ When peanuts are roasted well add dry coconut, cumin seeds and roast well until coconut 
  changes the color a little. 
‚Ä¢ When coconut turns light golden, turn off the gas and add fenugreek seeds. 
‚Ä¢ Transfer all the roasted ingredients into a blender jar and add kala masala, red chili powder, 
  salt, sugar and blend into a little coarse powder. 
‚Ä¢ You can use garam masala, goda masala or any other masala that you use regularly in place 
  of kala masala. 
‚Ä¢ You can use gudh in place of sugar or completely skip sugar too. 
‚Ä¢ Masala is ready. 
‚Ä¢ Heat up oil in a pan. 
‚Ä¢ Add onion and fry until it turns light golden. 
‚Ä¢ You can skip onion if you don‚Äôt like. 
‚Ä¢ When onion begins to turn light golden add capsicum and mix well. 
‚Ä¢ Cover and steam for about 6-7 minutes. 
‚Ä¢ Mix well at the regular intervals of 2-3 minutes. 
‚Ä¢ After about 6-7 minutes when capsicum is almost cooked add salt and mix well. 
‚Ä¢ Add 2-3 tsp masala that we blended and mix well. 
‚Ä¢ Cover and steam the sabzi on low heat for about 3-4 minutes.  
‚Ä¢ Add coriander leaves and mix well. 
‚Ä¢ Dhobli mirachi sabzi is all ready.

snippet.title: 11 Women Travelling To Goa For Vacation Die In Horrifying Road Accident In Karnataka's Dharwad
snippet.description:
women who were travelling to Goa on vacation and their driver were killed on Friday in a road accident in Karnataka‚Äôs Dharwad district after a minibus collided with a tipper truck along the Hubballi-Dharwad bypass near Itigatti. Among the deceased include the daughter-in-law of a former BJP MLA from Davangere‚Äôs Jagalur, Preethi Ravikumar. She is the daughter-in-law of former MLA Guru Siddanagouda. Dharwad Sub-urban Police Inspector Yaligar said that the accident took place around 8 am on Friday when the mini bus collided with the tipper truck, which was coming from the opposite direction. 

A group of 16 women from Davangere, who were members of the Ladies Club, were travelling to Goa for a vacation, when the incident occurred. The Dharwad Rural Police said that the women had decided to visit the residence of their friend in Dharwad for breakfast and had decided to take a detour. The minibus was crossing the Hubbali-Dharwad bypass, when it collided into the tipper truck as there was not enough room on the road to maneuver, Inspector Yaligar said.

snippet.title: EMBRACING CHANGE | Building our Home at Cabin in Woods
snippet.description:
NEW YEAR, NEW EAMON & BEC! We are so excited for all of the adventures 2021 has in store for us all. Want to learn something new this year? The first 1000 people to use the link will get a free trial of Skillshare Premium Membership: https://skl.sh/eamonbec01211

‚ñ∫ SUBSCRIBE for a new video every single Sunday https://youtube.com/eamonbec?sub_confirmation=1
‚ñ∫ The vlog continues on Instagram https://instagram.com/eamonandbec

We've escaped to the wilderness & we're building our home at a cabin in the woods ... a phrase that we didn't think we'd be saying just one short year ago. But, if 2020 taught us anything it was to embrace change so with that spirit we are looking forward to all of the many blessings, lessons and love that 2021 has in store for us all. 
This week Eamon's does something we NEVER thought we'd see (remember that whole embracing chane thing?). Yeah, he chops off ALL his hair! Or does he ü§î ?. We also take you out onto our frozen lake to enjoy a very Canadian sport of ice skating! Plus, there's the never-ending renovations projects inside the cabin and a healthy dose of laughter. 

Catch up on our cabin in the woods videos: https://bit.ly/3mNAcpX

Thanks to Skillshare for sponsoring today's video!

Eamon & Bec Products
‚Ü† handmade chai blends https://chaiwalachai.com/ ‚Üû
‚Ü† cookbook https://bit.ly/3o8MSs2 ‚Üû
‚Ü† professional photo filters https://bit.ly/2HNyKES ‚Üû
‚Ü† van build guide https://bit.ly/37jUqkQ ‚Üû

Who are we?

We're Eamon and Bec, a Canadian couple who previously lived and traveled full-time in our self converted Sprinter Van!! When the pandemic hit earlier this year we made the difficult decision to abandon our van in Africa and fly home to Canada. Now we're here... living at a cabin in the Canadian wilderness. We've always envisioned moving into the woods by the lake and building our dream tiny cabin as a home base for us to come back to in between our international travels. We cannot wait to have a place to call our own!! 

Our goal here is to inspire you to chase after your own dreams! We hope to create a community of like-minded, positive individuals who will grow to love and support one another on their own journeys.

snippet.title: Hot Fire Engine Test for the Artemis Moon Rocket
snippet.description:
One step closer to Artemis missions to the Moon üöÄ ¬†We are targeting a two-hour test window that opens at 4 p.m. EST on Sat., Jan. 16 for the hot fire test of the Space Launch System (SLS) rocket core stage at our Stennis Space Center. The hot fire is the eighth and final test of the Green Run series, to ensure the core stage of the SLS is ready to launch #Artemis missions to the Moon. This will be the first time that all four RS-25 engines will be fired at once in order to simulate a launch, generating 1.6 million pounds of thrust.¬†

Live coverage begins at 3:20 p.m. EST. Use the hashtag #AskNASA and your questions might be answered on air üöÄ

snippet.title: EMBRACING CHANGE | Building our Home at Cabin in Woods
snippet.description:
NEW YEAR, NEW EAMON & BEC! We are so excited for all of the adventures 2021 has in store for us all. Want to learn something new this year? The first 1000 people to use the link will get a free trial of Skillshare Premium Membership: https://skl.sh/eamonbec01211

‚ñ∫ SUBSCRIBE for a new video every single Sunday https://youtube.com/eamonbec?sub_confirmation=1
‚ñ∫ The vlog continues on Instagram https://instagram.com/eamonandbec

We've escaped to the wilderness & we're building our home at a cabin in the woods ... a phrase that we didn't think we'd be saying just one short year ago. But, if 2020 taught us anything it was to embrace change so with that spirit we are looking forward to all of the many blessings, lessons and love that 2021 has in store for us all. 
This week Eamon's does something we NEVER thought we'd see (remember that whole embracing chane thing?). Yeah, he chops off ALL his hair! Or does he ü§î ?. We also take you out onto our frozen lake to enjoy a very Canadian sport of ice skating! Plus, there's the never-ending renovations projects inside the cabin and a healthy dose of laughter. 

Catch up on our cabin in the woods videos: https://bit.ly/3mNAcpX

Thanks to Skillshare for sponsoring today's video!

Eamon & Bec Products
‚Ü† handmade chai blends https://chaiwalachai.com/ ‚Üû
‚Ü† cookbook https://bit.ly/3o8MSs2 ‚Üû
‚Ü† professional photo filters https://bit.ly/2HNyKES ‚Üû
‚Ü† van build guide https://bit.ly/37jUqkQ ‚Üû

Who are we?

We're Eamon and Bec, a Canadian couple who previously lived and traveled full-time in our self converted Sprinter Van!! When the pandemic hit earlier this year we made the difficult decision to abandon our van in Africa and fly home to Canada. Now we're here... living at a cabin in the Canadian wilderness. We've always envisioned moving into the woods by the lake and building our dream tiny cabin as a home base for us to come back to in between our international travels. We cannot wait to have a place to call our own!! 

Our goal here is to inspire you to chase after your own dreams! We hope to create a community of like-minded, positive individuals who will grow to love and support one another on their own journeys.

Today TommyInnit, Wilbur Soot, Philza & more have lots of fun with the Natural Disaster Mod in Minecraft. It was properly mental.

Edited by Tommy + Huge Man Editor Yahi ( @Yahiamice )

@Wilbur Soot @Ph1LzA @JackManifoldTV @Tubbo 

Follow my Twitter - @tommyinnit

Follow my Instagram - @tommyinnitt

Today Me, Wilbur Soot, Tubbo, Jack Manifold & Philza Minecraft install the Natural Disaster Mod in Minecraft 1.16.4! Even though I had a Minecraft War with Dream on the Dream Team SMP Minecraft Server today Tubbo went crazy and he is just hilarious and we had lots of laughs. This was so fun, awesome, poggers and cool! This Minecraft Mod uses Natural Disasters which make the game so fun and cool but not Colorblind like GeorgeNotFound - thank god! I Love Minecraft fun. 
This video was inspired by Slimecicle who did another video first on this and it was very funny & poggers!

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin but it is me and my good friends playing the NEW FUNNIEST MINECRAFT MOD EVER!!! POG CHAMP!!!

snippet.title: What Retirement On $1,000-$2,000 A Month In Singapore Looks Like
snippet.description:
Can you enjoy retirement on S$1,000 to S$2,000 a month in Singapore? Three retired 60-somethings - a former IT professional, firefighter and salesman - share what life after retiring is like, and how they built their nest eggs.

ALSO WATCH: 
Am I Planning Right For Retirement, Even In A Recession? For Ages 30+ and 40+
https://youtu.be/KCYDIFDiHag
Retirement Planning When You're In Your 50s (And In A Recession)
https://youtu.be/Dnc8Bh9G_H0

On a budget of about S$2,000 a month, Phua Foo Guan leads an active lifestyle going running, stair-climbing, playing table tennis and travelling. He once made a 30-day trip to Beijing, Siberia, Moscow and St Petersburg on a carefully-planned budget, and has also been to Cuba, Mexico and Alaska with his wife. He has been saving in cash and CPF since young, and investing his money over the years.

After working hard and scrapping by to put his four children through university, former airport firefighter Mohd Amin now enjoys time with family and friends - a modest lifestyle that requires only some S$1,000 a month. Downgrading from their 5-room to a 2-room HDB flat helped ensure a comfortable nest-egg.

Patrick Lee, who is single, found more time in retirement to care for his mum who has dementia. His budget of S$1,200 a month lets him take regular short holidays to Vietnam or Phuket, and indulge in cooking for friends or champagne brunches. His retirement income includes unit trust dividends and cash from renting out a room in his HDB flat.

To start planning for your retirement, visit https://cpf.gov.sg/BeReady

Episode 02 : Master
Episode Summary : 
Showing his talent in magic when he's only 3 years old, Rudeus's family hires him a tutor. Master Roxy, the surly loli with scornful eyes. With her magic lessons, Rudeus's magic is developing rapidly. Time flies, and one day Roxy holds an exam for Rudeus. However, Rudeus needs to overcome his trauma from beforelife for this exam.

snippet.title: Flight recorders found after Indonesia plane crash | DW News
snippet.description:
Indonesian search teams have located the black-box flight recorders of a passenger plane that crashed into the Java Sea on Saturday. 62 people were on board the Boeing 737-500 aircraft. Authorities now hope the black box data will clarify why the plane came down only minutes after taking off from Jakarta.Indonesian search and rescue teams are sorting through debris found by divers in the Java Sea. Body parts and children's clothes were among the first items retrieved from the water. Divers also located the plane's black box recorder, confirming the debris is from the missing Boeing 737-500.Still hoping for unlikely good news, the relatives of the 62 people on board meet with authorities, where they hand over DNA to help identify potential victims. The Sriwijaya Air flight left Jakarta airport on Saturday, bound for a 90 minute journey to Pontianak. But it lost contact only minutes after takeoff, data from online service FlightRadar24 shows the plane suddenly losing altitude and speed. Boats will continue to search the ocean, as authorities try to piece together what happened to flight SJ 182. Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1

snippet.title: Putra Sulung Syekh Ali Jaber Ungkap Pesan Terakhir sang Ayah sebelum Wafat, Minta Tak Ingkari 1 Hal
snippet.description:
TRIBUN-VIDEO.COM - Putra sulung pendakwah Syekh Ali Jaber, Al Hasan Ali Jaber mengungkapkan wasiat terakhir sang ayah.

Hasan mengaku terakhir kali bertemu sang ayah kurang lebih dua minggu lalu.

Ia lantas mengungkapkan bagaimana pesan terakhir Syekh Ali Jaber sebelum sang ayah meninggal dunia.

Dikutip dari TribunWow.com, ditemui di rumah duka di Lombok Nusa Tenggara Barat, Hasan tampak duduk di depan rumah bersama pelayat lain.

Meski tengah dirundung duka, Hasan masih bisa menjawab pertanyaan dari awak media.

Hasan menjelaskan, ia terakhir kali bertemu sang ayah dua minggu lalu di rumah sakit.

Terakhir itu sebelum masuk rumah sakit, kurang lebih dua minggu di rumah sakit," kata Hasan.

"Dia sebelum ke rumah sakit itu ketemu, dia udah positif (Covid-19) diambil ke rumah sakit, habis itu enggak pernah ketemu lagi," ungkapnya.

Hasan bercerita, mengetahui kabar meninggalnya sang ayah sekira pukul 10.00 WITA.

Ia pun membenarkan wasiat terakhir Syekh Ali Jaber yang ingin dimakamkan di Lombok.

Hasan mengaku sedang mengupayakan hal tersebut dan berharap tak ada kendala dalam persiapan tersebut.

"Iya, kita usahain, lagi diurus dulu, belum ada kabar," kata Hasan.

Sempat berkomunikasi dengan sang ayah, Hasan mengaku Syekh Ali Jaber telah memberikan pesan terakhir padanya.

Ia meminta agar Hasan menjaga sang ibu, Umi Nadia dan kedua adiknya.

Syekh Ali Jaber juga mengingatkan sang putra untuk selalu menjalankan salat.

Pasalnya, salat adalah pondasi untuk dapat mendirikan agama islam yang kokoh.

"Jaga salat sama jaga mama," kata Hasan.

"Yang penting salat."

"Dia cuma pesannya yang penting jangan tinggalin salat, karena pondasi agama," lanjutnya.

Hasan menuturkan, cukup aktif berkomunikasi dengan sang ayah sebelum dipindahkan ke ruang ICU.

Hasan menuturkan, sejak sang ulama masuk ke ruang khusus, komunikasi mereka terputus hingga hari kematiannya.

Hasan juga menyebutkan bahwa dirinya tak bisa menjenguk sang ayah lantaran ketentuan protokol kesehatan terkait status Syekh Ali Jaber yang positiv terpapar Virus Corona.

"Terakhir itu sebelum masuk ICU masih pegang hp beliau," kata Hasan.  

"Setelah masuk ICU sudah enggak, enggak bisa (menjenguk), protokol," pungkasnya.

Pendakwah Ali Saleh Mohammed Ali Jaber diketahui meninggal dunia Kamis (14/1/2021) di Rumah Sakit Yarsi, Cempaka Putih, Jakarta Pusat.

Syekh Ali Jaber menghembuskan napas terakhir 08.30 WIB di ruang ICU.

Sebelumnya Syekh Ali Jaber sempat dinyatakan positif Covid-19.

Namun informasi terakhir, kondisinya dikabarkan membaik.

(Tribun-Video.com)

snippet.title: Chaos in Washington as Trump supporters storm Capitol and force lockdown of Congress - BBC News
snippet.description:
Thousands of supporters of President Trump have stormed the US Capitol building, venting their anger at the victory of Joe Biden in the presidential election. 

They forced the evacuation and lockdown of Congress, where lawmakers were preparing to approve the election result. 

Shortly before the clashes President Trump had addressed his supporters near the White House telling them that he would never accept defeat. 

President-elect Biden called on Mr Trump to tell his people to go home and eventually that was the message delivered from the White House.

Washington‚Äôs Mayor ordered a curfew as members of the US National Guard were deployed to protect the city. 

Huw Edwards presents BBC News at Ten reporting by North America editor Jon Sopel in Washington and from Aleem Maqbool and Lebo Diseko at the Capitol.

snippet.title: Trump branded ‚Äúembarrassment to his country‚Äù as he shuns Biden inauguration - BBC News
snippet.description:
President Trump has announced he won't be attending the inauguration of his successor, Joe Biden,  just hours after promising a peaceful transition. 

He  will become the first US president to miss the ceremony in more than 150 years. 

Joe Biden said the decision was a good thing and it was one of the only things they'd ever agreed on. He said President Trump was an embarrassment to his country. 

Sophie Raworth presents BBC News at Ten reporting by North America editor Jon Sopel.

snippet.title: Galaxy S21 Ultra: Official Introduction Film | Samsung
snippet.description:
Designed to be epic in every way, with a revolutionary camera experience and powerful performance.

Introducing the new #Samsung #GalaxyS21 Ultra.

[Design]
Galaxy S21 Ultra‚Äôs bold new contour-cut camera design in a category of its own. And the new Phantom Black color only adds to its allure.

[Camera]
Galaxy S21 Ultra revolutionizes all a camera can do. With the highest resolution video available on a smartphone, you can now pull epic hi-res photos straight from 8K video. With 8K Video Snap,  you won‚Äôt miss the moment choosing between photo and video.

Ground-breaking Director‚Äôs View reimagines movie making. Simply switch between camera angles, from ultra-wide to wide, go close with tele or select Vlogger Mode to put yourself in the film. And at 60fps in 4K across all four lenses, every move now looks super smooth. 

Epic high resolution doesn‚Äôt stop at video. Enhanced 108MP sensor captures true-to-life photos with rich colors. The brilliant shots continue in Night Mode as AI deep learning and multi-frame blending transform after dark adventures into bright, vivid photos. 

[Performance]
Galaxy S21 Ultra runs the fastest chip in Galaxy. 2x faster NPU with enhanced GPU and CPU deliver category-leading speeds, enabling its epic Pro-grade camera to seamlessly handle the highest resolution photos and videos possible. It even manages the 5000mAh battery more intelligently so it outlasts the day, even on 5G. 

[Display]
When scrolling through your feed at speed, Galaxy S21 Ultra‚Äôs 120Hz Intelligent Display adapts refresh rates to what you‚Äôre watching, making battery way more efficient too. Eye Comfort Shield intelligently adjusts blue light for you. 

[S Pen]
And with the first S Pen compatible for Galaxy S Series, you‚Äôve got an entirely new level of precision editing at your fingertips. Perfect for trimming videos to the exact frame, S Pen will revolutionize how you craft your videos and images. 

Learn more: http://smsng.co/S21U_Intro_yt

Here comes The Big Bulls Stars, Ajay Devang, Abhishek Bachchan, Sohum Shah, and Nikita Dutta are on the Set of The Kapil Sharma Show and have a huge laughter ride, sharing their experiences of working with each other. Catch the fun.

Kapil Sharma is back with a new 'Salah Center' (Consultancy Business) in a Mohollah with absurd characters. snippet.title: Trump branded ‚Äúembarrassment to his country‚Äù as he shuns Biden inauguration - BBC News
snippet.description:
President Trump has announced he won't be attending the inauguration of his successor, Joe Biden,  just hours after promising a peaceful transition. 

He  will become the first US president to miss the ceremony in more than 150 years. 

Joe Biden said the decision was a good thing and it was one of the only things they'd ever agreed on. He said President Trump was an embarrassment to his country. 

Sophie Raworth presents BBC News at Ten reporting by North America editor Jon Sopel.

snippet.title: Chaos in Washington as Trump supporters storm Capitol and force lockdown of Congress - BBC News
snippet.description:
Thousands of supporters of President Trump have stormed the US Capitol building, venting their anger at the victory of Joe Biden in the presidential election. 

They forced the evacuation and lockdown of Congress, where lawmakers were preparing to approve the election result. 

Shortly before the clashes President Trump had addressed his supporters near the White House telling them that he would never accept defeat. 

President-elect Biden called on Mr Trump to tell his people to go home and eventually that was the message delivered from the White House.

Washington‚Äôs Mayor ordered a curfew as members of the US National Guard were deployed to protect the city. 

Huw Edwards presents BBC News at Ten reporting by North America editor Jon Sopel in Washington and from Aleem Maqbool and Lebo Diseko at the Capitol.

snippet.title: The Hoonicorn's Last Ride? Ken Block's Final Drive in the 1400hp AWD Mustang Hoonicorn V2
snippet.description:
Ken Block and Ford Motor Company‚Äôs exclusive partnership has brought in some real hardware over the past decade in rally and rallycross. 19 race wins plus 17 other podium finishes, 2 X Games medals, well over a billion video views across Block‚Äôs social media platforms, and the first ever World Rally Championship points scored for the brand by an American driver. As of January 2021, that exclusivity comes to an end, with Block becoming a free agent. And that means his options behind the wheel are now wide open. 

‚ÄúWorking  with Ford over the past decade has been awesome.‚Äù says Ken Block. ‚ÄúFrom racing all over the world, to accumulating  a half billion views from Gymkhana THREE to Gymkhana TEN, to creating the Emmy nominated series The Gymkhana Files for Amazon Prime - along with building a fleet of Fords including the iconic AWD Mustang Hoonicorn and F-150 Hoonitruck - it‚Äôs been a great partnership. It‚Äôs simply been a dream come true to work with the company that built the truck that my Dad drove when I was a teenager. I‚Äôm super appreciative to Ford for the support over the years, but I am also looking forward to what an unrestricted 2021 holds, and the ability to spread my wings a bit and play with a lot other toys.

2020 was a big year for Block and his Ford vehicles. He took the overall win at Rally Barbados in a WRC2 Ford Fiesta, won his class (and 3rd overall) at Rally Legend in San Marino in his Ford Escort Cossie V2, and also won the first ever Projekt E race of the FIA World RallyCross Championship in Holjes, Sweden, in a Ford Fiesta. Along with winning races, Block and Hoonigan launched the all-new viral video series,- Hoonicorn Vs The World. Spanning 11 episodes, the series features Ken racing his 1965 Ford Mustang RTR Hoonicorn against a variety of wild vehicles including a McLaren Senna and the World‚Äôs Fastest Donk. The series has been viewed over 34 million times since its launch in late November. 

What does the next chapter have in store? Ken Block and Hoonigan Racing Division will be announcing new partnerships very soon. In the meantime, enjoy this video of Ken‚Äôs favorite Ford ‚Äì the 1,400 horsepower AWD Mustang Hoonicorn V2 ‚Äì get taken on its ‚Äúlast ride‚Äù.

snippet.localized.title: The Hoonicorn's Last Ride? Ken Block's Final Drive in the 1400hp AWD Mustang Hoonicorn V2
snippet.localized.description:
Ken Block and Ford Motor Company‚Äôs exclusive partnership has brought in some real hardware over the past decade in rally and rallycross. 19 race wins plus 17 other podium finishes, 2 X Games medals, well over a billion video views across Block‚Äôs social media platforms, and the first ever World Rally Championship points scored for the brand by an American driver. As of January 2021, that exclusivity comes to an end, with Block becoming a free agent. And that means his options behind the wheel are now wide open. 

‚ÄúWorking  with Ford over the past decade has been awesome.‚Äù says Ken Block. ‚ÄúFrom racing all over the world, to accumulating  a half billion views from Gymkhana THREE to Gymkhana TEN, to creating the Emmy nominated series The Gymkhana Files for Amazon Prime - along with building a fleet of Fords including the iconic AWD Mustang Hoonicorn and F-150 Hoonitruck - it‚Äôs been a great partnership. It‚Äôs simply been a dream come true to work with the company that built the truck that my Dad drove when I was a teenager. I‚Äôm super appreciative to Ford for the support over the years, but I am also looking forward to what an unrestricted 2021 holds, and the ability to spread my wings a bit and play with a lot other toys.

2020 was a big year for Block and his Ford vehicles. He took the overall win at Rally Barbados in a WRC2 Ford Fiesta, won his class (and 3rd overall) at Rally Legend in San Marino in his Ford Escort Cossie V2, and also won the first ever Projekt E race of the FIA World RallyCross Championship in Holjes, Sweden, in a Ford Fiesta. Along with winning races, Block and Hoonigan launched the all-new viral video series,- Hoonicorn Vs The World. Spanning 11 episodes, the series features Ken racing his 1965 Ford Mustang RTR Hoonicorn against a variety of wild vehicles including a McLaren Senna and the World‚Äôs Fastest Donk. The series has been viewed over 34 million times since its launch in late November. 

What does the next chapter have in store? Ken Block and Hoonigan Racing Division will be announcing new partnerships very soon. In the meantime, enjoy this video of Ken‚Äôs favorite Ford ‚Äì the 1,400 horsepower AWD Mustang Hoonicorn V2 ‚Äì get taken on its ‚Äúlast ride‚Äù.

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Vend√©e Globe: Schafft der Deutsche Boris Herrmann die Sensation? | SPORTreportage - ZDF
snippet.description:
Seit mehr als zwei Monaten jagen die Yachten bei der Segel-Regatta Vend√©e Globe um die Welt. F√ºr die Spitzengruppe um Boris Herrmann r√ºckt die Heimat allm√§hlich n√§her - rund 6.000 Kilometer hat Herrmann noch vor sich.

Jede Woche laden wir hier eine neue Episode unserer Doku-Serie √ºber die Vend√©e Globe hoch. Alle Episoden findet ihr in der ZDFmediathek. Dort geht die neueste Folge auch immer schon ein bisschen fr√ºher online als hier bei YouTube: https://www.zdf.de/sport#xtor=CS3-72

ZDFsport abonnieren? Hier klicken http://kurz.zdf.de/sportabo/ 
ZDFsport bei Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/zdfsport/
ZDFsport bei Facebook: https://de-de.facebook.com/ZDFsport/ 

Der Deutsche Boris #Herrmann hat die Welt bereits dreimal im Team umsegelt, aber noch nie alleine. Er trainiert seit Jahren mit der franz√∂sischen Einhand-Elite, beherrscht mittlerweile die franz√∂sische Sprache und gilt als Top-Ten-Aspirant. F√ºr Herrmann, den "L‚ÄôAllemand", hat das Ankommen h√∂chste Priorit√§t.

Der Kurs der #Vend√©eGlobe ist mit seinen S√ºdpolarmeer-Passagen 24.296 Seemeilen (das entspricht 44.996 Kilometern) lang und durch schwere St√ºrme und haushohe Wellen schwierig zu bew√§ltigen. Von bislang 167 Teilnehmern haben in den ersten acht Auflagen der Vend√©e Globe nur 89 das Ziel erreicht. Viele gaben vorher auf. Die durchschnittliche Ausfallquote liegt bei 46 Prozent. Den Rekord f√ºr die schnellste Vend√©e-Globe-Runde hat Armel Le Cl√©ac‚Äôh 2017 mit 74 Tagen, 3 Stunden und 36 Minuten aufgestellt. 

Beim diesj√§hrigen Rennen sind 27 Skipper und sechs Skipperinnen an den Start gegangen, um die Weltumseglung alleine, ohne Zwischenstopp und ohne Hilfe von au√üen in etwa 70 Tagen zu bew√§ltigen. Der Kurs f√ºhrt die Flotte von Frankreich √ºber den Atlantik hinunter bis ins S√ºdpolarmeer, entlang der drei gro√üen Kaps ‚Äì dem Kap der Guten Hoffnung, Kap Leuwin und Kap Hoorn ‚Äì und wieder den Atlantik hinauf in den Start- und Zielhafen Les Sables-d‚ÄôOlonne. Der franz√∂sische Einhand-Klassiker z√§hlt neben dem America's Cup, dem Ocean Race und der olympischen Regatta zu den vier bedeutendsten Segelrennen der Welt.

Zweite Show, zweite Pr√ºfung. Zoe Saip, Frank Fussbroich und Mike Heiter m√ºssen dieses Mal ihre Dschungelcamp-Tauglichkeit beim "Dekodieren" unter Beweis stellen. Doch Zahlencodes in Kombination mit fiesen kleinen Viechern sind so gar nicht ihr Ding. Es treten zwar alle drei Kandidaten an ‚Äì doch keiner ist erfolgreich. Zu langsam und (f√ºr Zoe) auch zu eklig. Wir zeigen das 0 Sterne-Desaster im Video.

Zoe findet's ‚Äûultra eklig‚Äú
Jeder der drei Dschungelshow-Kandidaten hat drei Minuten Zeit, Zahlencodes in einer Box frei zu legen. Die m√ºssen sich gemerkt werden, um damit Schl√∂sser auf zu kriegen. Problem: Die Zahlencodes sind in einer Box mit Tierchen wie Vogelspinnen, Schlangen, Kakerlaken und Co. Zoe Saip f√§ngt an und hat so gar keinen Spa√ü am Kontakt mit den tierischen Bewohnern und Innereien ihrer Box: "Ultra eklig, sorry!" Das Model knackt schlie√ülich doch einen Code und probiert sein Gl√ºck bei den Zahlenschl√∂ssern. Ohne Erfolg. Der Code war eine der wenigen Nieten. Also wieder mit den H√§nden in die tierische Box ‚Äì leider wird auch das nichts. Keine Sterne f√ºr Zoe ‚Äì aber immerhin hat sie nicht so laut gekreischt wie beim ersten Pr√ºfungsversuch in Show 1.

Frank findet's ‚Äûschei√üe!‚Äú
Frank Fussbroich versucht es als n√§chster. Er muss die Codes inmitten von Schlangen finden. Der 52-J√§hrige geht ruhig zu Werke, hat aber Probleme, die Schl√∂sser korrekt zu bedienen. Und dann ist seine Zeit auch schon rum: "Schei√üe!". Korrekt.

Mike findet: ‚ÄûIch war langsam, aber trotzdem schnell‚Äú
Kann Mike Heiter noch was rei√üen? Er war schon in der ersten Pr√ºfung der einzige, der Sterne holen konnte. Er bekommt es mit Vogelspinnen zu tun. Mike stellt sich zwar geschickt an, aber auch er hat kein Gl√ºck bei den freigelegten Codes. Immerhin schafft er es als einziger des Pr√ºfungs-Trios √ºberhaupt ein Schloss zu √∂ffnen, aber das reicht nicht, um die Sterne zu befreien.

Daniel findet: ‚Äû0 Sterne sind in jedem Fall wenig‚Äú
Tja, leider eine absolute Nullnummer in Dschungel-Show 2 ‚Äì oder wie Mike sagt: "Ich war schon langsam, aber trotzdem schnell". Das lassen wir einfach mal so stehen. Daniel Hartwich nicht:"0 Sterne sind in jedem Fall aber wenig".

Naja, in Ausgabe 3 von "Ich bin ein Star ‚Äì Die gro√üe Dschungelshow" bekommen Zoe, Mike und Frank nochmal eine Chance auf Sterne.
